== Ingredients
- 6-8 apples
- 80mL apple cider vinegar
- 30g warm spices 
- sugar (optional)

== Directions
- Core, peel, and dice apples
- Boil apples in vinegar and spices with sugar until fork-tender
- Puree or mash until desired texture

